B.name: OrderID
B.description:
The order to get the fulfillment options for.

This is the ID of a `Order`

B.name: SupportedOptions
B.description:
The options the client supports for picking the fulfillment options.
This is for backwards compatibility purposes if a new option is added in the future so existing
options don't move to another set of options that the client can't handle yet.
Flags enum, combine any of the below values:

* `0` - NormalDelivery
* `1` - PickupDropoff
